if i am clsoing the shop at ith hour what do i need to know--> penalty before ith hour if shop is open till 0 to (i-1) + penalty from ith hour to last hour if shop is closed at ith hour..that is---->open_pre[i-1]+close_suf[i];

# Approach
prefix and suffix sum

