# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1) First make prefix sum array for both count of 'Y' and count of 'N'
-Keep 0 at index 0 of both of the array as at 0th hour shop is closed so no customer has visited at that time
2) Then calculate the penalty for each index or time and keep maintaining the minimum penalty index

penalty = Totalcustomers - customers till that hour + number of case till that hour where no customer has visited the shop

3)Return your minimum index

