we are counting Y and N freqency in the first loop then after that we are againg iterating through the same loop to find our ans.

$$T.C=O(n)+O(n)=2O(N) = O(n)$$

- Space complexity:
No extra space is used expext delaring prefix_n, suffix_y.

$$S.C = O(1)$$

