If You observe the given Example carefully you can see we are calculating the penalty at each index.We can easily think for a O(N^2) Solution by using 2 for loops.We can Optimise it if we check how we are calculating the penalty at each step its like if we close the shop at that given index, the penalty will be just counting the number of "N" before that index and number of "Y" current+after that Index.
# Approach
