# Approach
    Firstly count all the penalties(all 'N)
    Then traverse the string from right to left(from end)
    If ith is 'Y' then penalty++ else penalty--
    Check if penalty is smaller then ans or not
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(N)
